# Java Requirements
Java JDK 8 or above  
MySQL Connector/J (com.mysql.cj.jdbc.Driver)  

# Database
MySQL Server with the following tables:
    - menu (id INT, name VARCHAR, price DECIMAL)
    - staff (id INT, name VARCHAR, password_hash VARCHAR)
    - orders (id INT, table_no INT, status VARCHAR)
    - order_items (id INT, order_id INT, menu_item_id INT, quantity INT)

# External Libraries
mysql-connector-j-<version>.jar  (Add to project classpath)